       suckless: https://suckless.org
       sent: https://tools.suckless.org/sent/

1. open presentation with sent:
> sent prez

2. enjoy

(*) for changing background/foreground color go to:
> cd ~/sent

and open config.h script:
> nano config.h

then change background and foreground color (hex format)

save the config.h file and on the same path run:
> make clean
> make
> sudo make install
